data.text:
1- *denotes result stricken from NCAA records due to team violation by

Memphis-2008, Michigan-1992 & 1993, UCLA-1980, Villanova-1971.

4- City College of New York is now in Division 3.

5- Memphis State University name changed to University of Memphis

on 07/01/1994.

6- Texas Western College name changed to University of Texas at

El Paso on 03/31/1967.

7- Oklahoma Agricultural and Mechanical College (Oklahoma A&M)

name was changed to Oklahoma State on May 15, 1957 3- NCAA officials records do not identify all assignments. In those cases,

possible game participation is indicated by slash (/) with official name.
